author: Jay Peters
title: Google extends free access to advanced teleconferencing features to September 30th
description: Google has announced that it will extend free access to some advanced Google Meet features to all G Suite and G Suite for Education customers until September 30th. Previously, Google said it would offer free access until July 1st.
content:
The advanced Meet features were previously free until July 1st
